title: Fantasy Week: Late-round league winners with Evan Silva (Football 8/28)
description:
Fantasy Week concludes as Will Brinson welcomes Evan Silva of Establish the Run to chat all things fantasy. The guys discuss strategy and stats followed by some mid-to-late round sleepers that could help you win your leagues this season. Who is worth buying into based on their market? We've discussed rookie running backs this week, now it's time for rookie wide receivers. And don't go forgetting about Jimmy Garoppolo...
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
